Flask Registration Form Project

Project Overview
This project is a Flask based web application that has user registration and success form.

The application allows user to:
1. Register using name, email and password
2. submit form data using POST method
3. Redirect to success page after submission
4. Apply styling using bootstrap

#Technology used
1. Python
2. Flask
3. HTML 5
4. BootStrap

#Project Structure
Flask Registration Project
|--templates
|  |----base.html
|  |----register.html
|  |----success.html
|--venv
|--app.py

#Installation and Setup Steps
1. Install Python
2. Create Virtual Environment
    $python -m venv venv
3. Activate the virtual Environment
    $.\venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
4. Install Flask
    $ pip install Flask
5. Verify the basic required libraries are installed or not
    $ pip list
6. Run the application
    $ python app.py

#Application workflow
1. Open any web browser
    http://127.0.0.1:5000
2. User Registration page will open
3. Enter the Name, Email and Password
4. Click on the submit button
5. User will redirected to success page
6. Username is dynamically displayed using the template variables


